### Donor API Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api

### Get My Matched Requests
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/my-matched-requests
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

### Accept Blood Request
PUT http://localhost:5000/donor-api/accept-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

{
  "requestNumber": "REQ-2026-00001"
}

### Complete Donation
PUT http://localhost:5000/donor-api/complete-donation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

{
  "requestNumber": "REQ-2026-00001"
}

### Get Donation History
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/donation-history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

### Get My Badges
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/badges
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

### Get Leaderboard (public)
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/leaderboard

### Get Top Donors (public)
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/top-donors

### Get My Rank
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/my-rank
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

### Get My Achievements
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/achievements
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

### Donor Dashboard
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

### Get My Accepted Requests
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/my-accepted-requests
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN

### Get My Matched Requests
GET http://localhost:5000/donor-api/my-matched-requests
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_DONOR_TOKEN
